<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 04:10:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶伦表示，美国和中国需要“艰难”的对话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-china-need-tough-conversations-yellen-tells/articleshow/109099837.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099837.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在与中国总理李强会面时强调了进行艰难讨论的重要性。李克强也强调了两国之间相互尊重和伙伴关系的必要性。耶伦强调管理华盛顿和北京之间错综复杂的关系的共同责任，特别是解决了对中国工厂产能过剩的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/us-china-need-tough-conversations-yellen-tells/articleshow/109099837.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本将加入 Aukus 的扩张计划以威慑中国：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/japan-to-join-aukus-in-expected-expansion-to-deter-china-report/articleshow/109099140.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099140.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国、英国和澳大利亚将扩大奥库斯协议，将日本纳入其对华威慑战略的一部分。消息人士证实，奥库斯国防部长将宣布就该协议的“第二支柱”进行会谈，重点是量子计算、海底技术、高超音速、人工智能和网络能力方面的联合开发。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:39:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/japan-to-join-aukus-in-expected-expansion-to-deter-china-report/articleshow/109099140.cms</guid></item><item><title>尽管遭遇挫折，美国核工业仍对小型反应堆持乐观态度</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nuclear-industry-upbeat-on-small-reactors-despite-setback/articleshow/109099571.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099571.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管 NuScale 在美国核项目中遭遇挫折，但无碳电力项目的希望依然存在。积极的前景包括 GE Hitachi 设计的 BWRX-300 和田纳西河谷管理局的投资。努力的目标是标准化和降低成本。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-nuclear-industry-upbeat-on-small-reactors-despite-setback/articleshow/109099571.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦正义运动党提名阿里·扎法尔为参议院反对党领袖候选人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-nominates-ali-zafar-as-candidate-for-opposition-leader-in-senate/articleshow/109099560.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099560.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-tehreek-e-insaf-nominates-ali-zafar-as-candidate-for-opposition-leader-in-senate/articleshow/109099560.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国派遣皇家海军舰艇加强对加沙的援助并建立新的海上走廊</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sends-royal-navy-ship-to-boost-aid-for-gaza-and-set-up-a-new-maritime-corridor/articleshow/109099186.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109099186.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 02:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sends-royal-navy-ship-to-boost-aid-for-gaza-and-set-up-a-new-maritime-corridor/articleshow/109099186.cms</guid></item><item><title>载有南卡罗来纳大学兄弟会的巴士在密西西比州发生翻车事故 11人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098641.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;密西西比州圣路易斯湾附近发生一起涉及南卡罗来纳大学学生的巴士事故，造成 11 人受伤。司机蒂娜·威尔逊和一名学生受重伤，其他人被送往医院。威尔逊的敏捷思维和学生保罗·克鲁恩的干预避免了一场潜在的灾难。该大学正在为受影响的学生提供支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭黎巴嫩真主党训练营</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列对黎巴嫩东部贝卡谷地的一个真主党训练营进行了空袭。真主党击落一架以色列无人机后，紧张局势升级。巴勒贝克附近的萨弗里镇遭到袭击，没有人员伤亡报告。真主党证实了无人机被击落的消息，并强调了持续的敌对行动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗发生4.3级地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098039.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</guid></item><item><title>“继续支持以色列”：苏纳克表示以色列与哈马斯的冲突“必须结束”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097369.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克支持以色列与哈马斯的冲突，呼吁结束暴力并释放人质。敦促加沙人道主义暂停，提及伤亡情况，并强调英国公众情绪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元支持伊朗和巴基斯坦的阿富汗移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097042.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元援助伊朗和巴基斯坦境内的阿富汗移民，以应对阿富汗的严峻形势。该报告预计到 2024 年将向 480 万阿富汗移民和 250 万收容社区成员提供援助，并强调迫切需要人道主义援助来帮助 2,370 万人生存。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</guid></item><item><title>彼得·佩莱格里尼赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096954.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在斯洛伐克，彼得·佩莱格里尼 (Peter Pellegrini) 以 53% 的支持率击败伊万·科尔科克 (Ivan Korcok) 的 47% 赢得总统选举。科尔科克优雅地认输，强调对结果的尊重。这次选举的焦点是对乌克兰冲突的不同看法，佩莱格里尼主张和谈。这场胜利反映了斯洛伐克在战争和外交上的立场。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国对阿富汗妇女和儿童营养不良激增发出警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096386.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国世界粮食计划署驻阿富汗办事处对妇女和儿童营养不良率不断上升表示担忧，喀布尔的营养不良病例在三年内增加了两倍。人道主义援助的减少加剧了这一问题，影响了营养不良患者的心理健康和设施。贫困、不安全和塔利班的限制使局势进一步恶化。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争已持续半年，特拉维夫爆发针对内塔尼亚胡的大规模抗议活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/massive-protests-in-tel-aviv-against-netanyahu-as-gaza-war-reaches-half-year-mark/articleshow/109096032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着加沙冲突进入第七个月，数万名以色列人在特拉维夫抗议，要求举行选举并要求内塔尼亚胡辞职。反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德批评领导层。据报道发生了冲突，并逮捕了一人。加沙人质家属参加示威，军队打捞第十二具人质尸体。冲突造成的死亡人数：加沙超过 33,000 人死亡，129 名人质幸存。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/massive-protests-in-tel-aviv-against-netanyahu-as-gaza-war-reaches-half-year-mark/articleshow/109096032.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽连斯基警告俄罗斯袭击导致防空能力不足</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-warns-of-air-defence-shortage-amid-russian-attacks/articleshow/109095807.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095807.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰总统泽连斯基对俄罗斯轰炸行动中的防空能力发出警告，强调爱国者系统的必要性。尽管面临平民伤亡和基础设施损坏，泽伦斯基仍然对美国国会的支持抱有希望，并对各种援助方案持开放态度。俄罗斯边境附近的冲突凸显了国际援助的紧迫性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-warns-of-air-defence-shortage-amid-russian-attacks/articleshow/109095807.cms</guid></item><item><title>艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统：以色列正在进行“血腥而艰难的战争”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-fighting-bloody-and-difficult-war-president-isaac-herzog/articleshow/109095574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统强调了冲突的严重性，因为以色列面临着六个月的里程碑。人质尸体的打捞和针对总理内塔尼亚胡管理的抗议活动增添了阴沉的基调。哈马斯袭击造成 1,170 人伤亡，人质仍被扣押在加沙。以色列的军事反应影响到平民，凸显了持久的冲突。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-fighting-bloody-and-difficult-war-president-isaac-herzog/articleshow/109095574.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国机构：导弹险些击中也门港口西南方向的船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missile-narrowly-misses-vessel-southwest-of-yemeni-port-uk-agency/articleshow/109095509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一枚导弹险些击中也门荷台达附近的一艘船只，但船员没有受伤。以美国为首的联军拦截了一枚导弹，另一枚则落入水中。胡塞叛军与以色列、英国和美国等国家之间的冲突不断升级。胡塞武装领导人承认伤亡并誓言瞄准红海航运。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missile-narrowly-misses-vessel-southwest-of-yemeni-port-uk-agency/articleshow/109095509.cms</guid></item><item><title>南佛罗里达州酒吧发生致命枪战，造成2人死亡、7人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/deadly-gunfight-at-south-florida-bar-leaves-2-dead-7-injured/articleshow/109095376.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095376.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;佛罗里达州多拉市一家酒吧发生致命枪战，造成两人死亡、七人受伤。顾客之间的冲突升级，导致一名保安被枪杀。多拉尔警察与袭击者交火，导致枪手死亡。调查正在进行中，以确定事件背后的动机。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/deadly-gunfight-at-south-florida-bar-leaves-2-dead-7-injured/articleshow/109095376.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯呼吁对“危险的”外德涅斯特无人机袭击事件进行调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-calls-for-investigation-into-dangerous-transdniestria-drone-attack/articleshow/109095357.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095357.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯批评无人机袭击了摩尔多瓦分离的外德涅斯特地区的一处军事设施，称这是出于对扩张担忧的挑衅。乌克兰军队击退了俄罗斯军队，缓解了人们的担忧。该事件引发了要求调查的呼声，德涅斯特河沿岸和摩尔多瓦处于高度戒备状态，凸显了地区紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-calls-for-investigation-into-dangerous-transdniestria-drone-attack/articleshow/109095357.cms</guid></item><item><title>蒙古9%的牲畜因冬季“dzuds”而损失</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/9-mongolia-livestock-lost-to-winter-dzuds/articleshow/109095350.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095350.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;气候变化加剧的极端冬季天气导致蒙古数百万头牲畜死亡，影响了严重依赖动物收入的游牧社区。联合国报告称，过去二十年来，蒙古的自然灾害增加了一倍，加剧了土地退化、荒漠化和水资源短缺，使牲畜在严冬中生存更加困难。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/9-mongolia-livestock-lost-to-winter-dzuds/articleshow/109095350.cms</guid></item><item><title>另一名印度学生在美国被发现死亡，引发担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/concerns-spiral-as-another-indian-student-found-dead-in-the-us/articleshow/109095341.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095341.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度学生乌玛·萨蒂亚·赛·加德 (Uma Satya Sai Gadde) 在美国克利夫兰去世，引发社会担忧。印度领事馆正在调查此案，并努力遣返她的遗体。全球印度教传统基金会呼吁联邦调查局对美国印度学生死亡事件进行独立调查，并通过在线请愿书收集支持。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/concerns-spiral-as-another-indian-student-found-dead-in-the-us/articleshow/109095341.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>